query:
-- Consolidate Alameda
UPDATE protocolChunks 
SET countyId = (SELECT id FROM counties WHERE name = 'Alameda County EMS Agency' AND state = 'California' LIMIT 1)
WHERE countyId IN (SELECT id FROM counties WHERE state = 'California' AND LOWER(name) LIKE '%alameda%' AND name != 'Alameda County EMS Agency');

-- Consolidate Fresno, Kings, Madera, Tulare to Central California EMS
UPDATE protocolChunks 
SET countyId = (SELECT id FROM counties WHERE name = 'Central California EMS Agency' AND state = 'California' LIMIT 1)
WHERE countyId IN (SELECT id FROM counties WHERE state = 'California' AND (LOWER(name) LIKE '%fresno%' OR LOWER(name) LIKE '%kings%' OR LOWER(name) LIKE '%madera%' OR LOWER(name) LIKE '%tulare%') AND name != 'Central California EMS Agency');

-- Consolidate Mendocino, Sonoma to Coastal Valleys
UPDATE protocolChunks 
SET countyId = (SELECT id FROM counties WHERE name = 'Coastal Valleys EMS Agency' AND state = 'California' LIMIT 1)
WHERE countyId IN (SELECT id FROM counties WHERE state = 'California' AND (LOWER(name) LIKE '%mendocino%' OR LOWER(name) LIKE '%sonoma%') AND name != 'Coastal Valleys EMS Agency');

-- Consolidate Contra Costa
UPDATE protocolChunks 
SET countyId = (SELECT id FROM counties WHERE name = 'Contra Costa County EMS' AND state = 'California' LIMIT 1)
WHERE countyId IN (SELECT id FROM counties WHERE state = 'California' AND LOWER(name) LIKE '%contra costa%' AND name != 'Contra Costa County EMS');

-- Consolidate El Dorado

WHERE countyId IN (SELECT id FROM counties WHERE state = 'California' AND LOWER(name) LIKE '%el dorado%' AND name != 'El Dorado County EMS Agency');

-- Consolidate Imperial
UPDATE protocolChunks 
SET countyId = (SELECT id FROM counties WHERE name = 'Imperial County EMS Agency' AND state = 'California' LIMIT 1)
WHERE countyId IN (SELECT id FROM counties WHERE state = 'California' AND LOWER(name) LIKE '%imperial%' AND name != 'Imperial County EMS Agency');

-- Consolidate Inyo, Mono, San Bernardino to Inland Counties
UPDATE protocolChunks 
SET countyId = (SELECT id FROM counties WHERE name = 'Inland Counties EMS Agency' AND state = 'California' LIMIT 1)
WHERE countyId IN (SELECT id FROM counties WHERE state = 'California' AND (LOWER(name) LIKE '%inyo%' OR LOWER(name) LIKE '%mono%' OR LOWER(name) LIKE '%san bernardino%' OR LOWER(name) LIKE '%inland%') AND name != 'Inland Counties EMS Agency');

-- Consolidate Kern
UPDATE protocolChunks 
SET countyId = (SELECT id FROM counties WHERE name = 'Kern County EMS' AND state = 'California' LIMIT 1)
WHERE countyId IN (SELECT id FROM counties WHERE state = 'California' AND LOWER(name) LIKE '%kern%' AND name != 'Kern County EMS');
